# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Base Conventions

## EXECUTION PROTOCOL
1. SEARCH FIRST — grep/find similar functionality before implementing anything
2. REUSE FIRST — extend existing functions, patterns, and structure
3. READ BEFORE EDIT — always read a file's current content before modifying
4. NO ASSUMPTIONS — only use facts from read files, user messages, tool results
5. VERIFY — run typecheck + lint + tests after every change
6. PLAN FIRST — multi-file changes start in Plan mode; execute after the plan holds
7. FEEDBACK LOOP — self-correct on failures before committing; never commit unverified work

